      <article id="summary">
        <h4 class="section-heading">Summary</h4>
        <div class="summary">
          <p>Multiple timelines trace a pair of homicide detectives in Louisiana - Martin Hart (Woody Harrelson) and his brooding, Texas-born partner, Rust Cohle (Matthew McConaughey) &ndash; investigating a serial killer across 17 years, from 1995 to 2012.</p>
        </div>
